: Restore HP (Uses Blood Vial)
: Strong attack Hold : Charge attack
When locked on to a target, you will quickstep instead of rolling.
: Use item : Toggle items
: Gestures : Personal Effects
Shooting your firearm will interrupt and stagger an enemy when properly timed to their attack.
Hitting an enemy from behind with a charge attack causes them to stagger.
when next to staggered enemy: Visceral attack
After taking damage from an enemy, there is a period of time in which attacking the enemy in return will restore a certain amount of your HP.
Receive assistance from the hunters of other worlds by using the Beckoning Bell.
Assist the hunters of other worlds by using the Small Resonant Bell.
The notes held by the messengers contain the written wit and wisdom of hunters from other worlds.
Entrusting your notes with the messengers will allow hunters from other worlds to read your words.
Ring the Beckoning Bell if you require assistance.
If you require assistance, you need only ring the bell.
If you require assistance, you need only ring the bell.
A Holy Chalice is said to be enshrined in Old Yharnam, seated in the valley.
To escape this dreadful Hunter's Dream, halt the source of the spreading scourge of beasts, lest the night carry on forever.
The red moon hangs low, and beasts rule the streets. Are we left no other choice, than to burn it all to cinders?
Madmen toil surreptitiously in rituals to beckon the moon. Uncover their secrets.
A watchman of Byrgenwerth guards the gate with a password, the sacred adage of the Grand Cathedral.
The Mensis ritual must be stopped, lest we all become beasts.
This way, to witness a miracle
